          <span class="accordion-item__title"
          >
            What are the different types of sim cards?
          </span>
          
            
              
                
              
            
          
        </button>
      </h4>
      
        
          <p class="">There are mainly 6 types of SIM cards: Full-Size SIM Cards (1FF), Mini SIM Cards (2FF), Micro SIM Cards (3FF), Nano SIM Cards (4FF), eSIM (Embedded SIM), and Integrated SIM.</p>
        
      

      
        
      

    </li>
  
    <li class="accordion-item">

      

      <h4 aria-level="3" role="heading" class="
          accordion-item__title-wrapper
          
          
          
