        >
          <span class="accordion-item__title"
          >
            What are the 3 types of SIM cards?
          </span>
          
            
              
                
              
            
          
        </button>
      </h4>
      
        
          <p class="">There are 3 types of SIM cards for phones: Mini-SIM (2FF), Micro SIM (3FF), and Nano SIM (4FF). Each one is smaller than the last, with the Nano SIM being the most commonly used in modern smartphones.</p>
        
      

      
        
      

    </li>
  
    <li class="accordion-item">

      

      <h4 aria-level="3" role="heading" class="
          accordion-item__title-wrapper
          
          
          
        "
      >
        <button
          class="accordion-item__click-target"
          aria-expanded="false"
          style="
