            padding-bottom: 30px;
            padding-left: 0px;
            padding-right: 0px;
          "
        >
          <span class="accordion-item__title"
          >
            Are there 2 types of SIM cards?
          </span>
          
            
              
                
              
            
          
        </button>
      </h4>
      
        
          <p class="">Broadly speaking, there are two main types of SIM cards: Physical SIM cards (Full-Size, Mini, Micro, and Nano SIMs) and Virtual SIM cards (eSIMs and Integrated SIMs). Physical SIM cards are removable, while Virtual SIM cards are either integrated into the device or exist solely digitally and don't require a physical card.</p>
        
      

      
        
      

